{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Commandant, the equipment and repair resources are ready.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "After countless inspections and investigations, I've made sure what happened last time won't happen again.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Good job, Lee.', 3: '7', 4: 'I knew I could count on you!', 5: '7'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Commandant, I heard that you've destroyed 500 Corrupted.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "The time it took certainly exceeded my expectations, but I'm a man of my word.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'What was that again?', 3: '10', 4: 'I still remember that promise.', 5: '10'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Take a guess.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Hallo Katty?', 3: '12'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "I don't know how you came up with something like that.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Do you want me to treat you like Kamui?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'A cat ears Lee?!', 3: '16'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "I'd be happy to show you the human electrochemical device in my room.", 4: '1'}
{2: "I'm out of ideas.", 3: '18'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "(Sighs) ...I knew you wouldn't be able to guess it.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Here, take it if you want.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Lee reveals an exquisite little robot that would dance when placed on your palm. It also comes with a handy alarm function.'}
{3: 'He turns back toward his workbench and continues to tinker with some parts.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Right, one more thing, if you decide to accept it, I won't forgive you if you lose it.", 4: '1'}
